<figureCitation id="1F0F1F4E494310A80E9554377A4C7E73" captionStart="Figure 7" captionStartId="F7" captionText="Figure 7. Cytospora schulzeri on Castanea mollissima (BJFC-S 1702). A, B Habit of conidiomata on branches C transverse section of conidiomata D longitudinal section through conidiomata E conidiogenous cells attached with conidia F conidia. Scale bars: 500 μm (B-D), 10 μm (E, F)." figureDoi="10.3897/mycokeys.62.47425.figure7" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/371658" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Figure 7</figureCitation>
